# Backend Status

Available Features:

✅ Authentication

✅ Daily Check-ins

✅ Dashboard

✅ Goals

✅ Habits

✅ Schedule Generator

---

# Backend Base URL

Local Development:

http://127.0.0.1:8000

Swagger Documentation:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

---


## 1. Authentication

### Login Page

Fields:

* Email
* Password

API:

POST /auth/login

### Signup Page

Fields:

* Email
* Password

API:

POST /auth/signup

---

# 2. Dashboard

After login navigate to Dashboard.

Display:

### Wellness Scores

* Mind Score
* Body Score
* Lifestyle Score
* Overall Score

### Burnout Status

* LOW
* MEDIUM
* HIGH

### Latest Check-in Summary

### Quick Actions

* Add Check-in
* Add Goal
* Add Habit
* Generate Schedule

API:

GET /dashboard/{user_id}

---

# 3. Daily Check-in Page

Purpose:

Collect daily wellness information.

Fields:

* Mood Score (1-10)
* Stress Level (1-10)
* Energy Level (1-10)
* Sleep Hours
* Water Intake
* Exercise Minutes
* Productivity Score (1-10)
* Notes

API:

POST /checkins

Request:

{
"user_id": "uuid",
"mood_score": 8,
"stress_level": 5,
"energy_level": 7,
"sleep_hours": 7,
"water_intake": 2.5,
"exercise_minutes": 30,
"productivity_score": 8,
"notes": "Feeling productive"
}

---

# 4. Goals Module

### Goal Creation

API:

POST /goals

Fields:

* Goal Name
* Category
* Target Date

### Goal List

API:

GET /goals/{user_id}

Display:

* Goal Name
* Category
* Progress %
* Status

### Goal Progress Update

API:

PATCH /goals/{goal_id}

Fields:

* Progress %
* Status

Suggested UI:

Progress Bar

---

# 5. Habits Module

### Create Habit

API:

POST /habits

Fields:

* Habit Name
* Category
* Target Frequency

Example:

* Study 2 Hours
* Daily Exercise
* Meditation

### View Habits

API:

GET /habits/{user_id}

### Log Habit Completion

API:

POST /habits/logs

Suggested UI:

Checkbox

Example:

☑ Study 2 Hours

☑ Drink Water

☐ Exercise

---

# 6. Schedule Module

### Generate Schedule

API:

POST /schedules/generate/{user_id}

Button:

Generate My Schedule

### View Schedule

API:

GET /schedules/{user_id}

Display:

Task Timeline

Example:

06:30 - Drink Water

07:00 - Morning Walk

09:00 - Study 2 Hours

20:00 - Meditation

---

# User Flow

Signup
↓
Login
↓
Dashboard
↓
Daily Check-in
↓
Scores Generated
↓
Burnout Prediction
↓
Goals
↓
Habits
↓
Generate Schedule
↓
View Schedule

---

# Authentication Flow

Login API returns:

{
"success": true,
"access_token": "...",
"refresh_token": "...",
"user": {
"id": "user_uuid",
"email": "[user@email.com](mailto:user@email.com)"
}
}

